# Local override for tests / tools run from this module's root.
#
# memql-bff-__PRODUCT__ is a library compiled into the memql binary;
# it has no main of its own. The .env here exists for symmetry with
# the other repos and for any test harness or generator that calls
# memql/component/genesis.ApplyLocalOverride("."). Copy this file to
# .env to use it; .env is gitignored.
#
# Authoritative source: memql/component/genesis/localenv.go.
#
# MEMQL_MASTER_KEY cannot be overridden here (genesis owns it).

# Observability verbosity propagated to anything spun up under this
# module's tests.
# MEMQL_OBSERVE_LEVEL=verbose
